{"tid":2138051,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警隊人手調動","createTime":"2020-08-03T10:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T12:07:13.000Z","uid":162103,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d70e7f0783f30660d71b4d70da63ca983abb2e1","tid":2138051,"uid":162103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:48:05.000Z","msg":"#警隊新調動<br />\n<br />\n警隊公共關係科再有新調動，高級警司江永祥及警司高振邦今個月會調離公共關係科，江永祥原職位將由原駐守鐵路警區指揮官梁仲文接手，而高振邦的原職位將由人事部總督察張家寶接手。<br />\n<br />\n媒體聯絡及傳訊高級警司江永祥在去年「反修例抗爭」期間多次出席警察記者會，由於經常要「er.........er........er.....」所以被網民稱為「er er Sir」，主力交代警方數字及應答傳媒提問。他將調任至香港輔警總部的輔警支援課。<br />\n<br />\n接手「Er Sir」的張仲文今年42歲，港大工商管理First Hon畢業，曾任IT公司顧問，01年加入警隊。<br />\n<br />\n至於高振邦將調至警察機動部隊受訓4個月，未來將帶領169人大隊，受訓後會到行動部應變大隊守3個月，再到「西九總區」機動部隊駐守，成為防暴警其中一員。<br />\n<br />\n接手高振邦的是46歲的張家寶，大學未畢業就投考警隊，曾任《警訊》主持。<br />\n<br />\n#高振邦 #江永祥 #警察新調動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/374743129763458/posts/727762137794887/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F374743129763458%2Fposts%2F727762137794887%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=5aabdb71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/374743129763458/posts/727762137794887/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"a8aa0a412def95d0e86060963b933649f36961ce","tid":2138051,"uid":108016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"照入制裁名單"},{"pid":"1dc3e97573733646d485c2c8a9aca4d23f4c1d60","tid":2138051,"uid":162103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:50:19.000Z","msg":"別讓江江跑掉"},{"pid":"b63c670f327bf68e6458f49a54e46760d5b904f3","tid":2138051,"uid":74418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"調職都要制裁"},{"pid":"6b850a821caa4fdcaa651a8d819d444584304853","tid":2138051,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"咁Er狗調去邊啊？定請長期病假去接受語語治療啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f9a873e16f94ce56b787ef9e0ce464100826cb","tid":2138051,"uid":162103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b850a821caa4fdcaa651a8d819d444584304853","tid":2138051,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"咁Er狗調去邊啊？定請長期病假去接受語語治療啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:58:17.000Z","msg":"輔警總部"},{"pid":"a5d6dc4108107faf61ca13af8c0088955abf9c8c","tid":2138051,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b850a821caa4fdcaa651a8d819d444584304853","tid":2138051,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"咁Er狗調去邊啊？定請長期病假去接受語語治療啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:58:43.000Z","msg":"睇漏眼 原來調去支援輔警 搵隻全職狗去支援兼職狗 不如索性調去守水塘咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d01a369795de96f256aaeabcdfe5ed35ad00db","tid":2138051,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"鐵路警區指揮官梁仲文<br />\n<br />\n[831]逾百抗爭者太子站黑夜路軌逃亡的真相!從不存在的地底人!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1831411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1831411</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190901/UEY5W5NMP3IGEF35VQ4TS54XDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190901%2FUEY5W5NMP3IGEF35VQ4TS54XDI%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=4c4fab6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190901%2FUEY5W5NMP3IGEF35VQ4TS54XDI%2F&h=7bb7ac9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190901/UEY5W5NMP3IGEF35VQ4TS54XDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n事由<br />\n<strong>當日有人自稱831苦主報料比apple「我地（哋）百幾人行緊地鐵路軌走，有好多傷者，而家個個站都有防暴等緊我地（哋），大圍捕」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實大家知唔知黑警有n個警區<br />\n其中一個狗力好足, 狗隊好自豪的叫鐵路狗區<br />\n你成百人走當班狗唔識call機夾你,黑警惡毒=/=智障<br />\n事後有人書面問apple 記者班人最後點而apple完全無回應, 因為報料人過去/現在乃至未來皆查無此人<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">真相好可能係831傷者部分早已不在人世,政府要製作一個故事合理化呢班人的消失</span></strong><br />\n831連日封站就係要把逆向用科學方法清洗現場, 永遠消滅死者曾在現場出現的痕跡"},{"pid":"324bb983d95be50b4fecd9d26ffb2e845d630a5c","tid":2138051,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:01:51.000Z","msg":"指揮消滅831證據,事後故佈疑陣好可能係鐵路狗區指揮官梁仲文<br />\n應該無其他人攬上身幫人抹屎<br />\n<br />\n果然手上無香港人的血係無得升"},{"pid":"64587e3c21a7b0a49b819a694c0056f6a9243668","tid":2138051,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:56:44.000Z","msg":"推 唔好俾個仆街走"},{"pid":"20a49bb85724ae305eb568668c2a40850ef3d7d6","tid":2138051,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc3e97573733646d485c2c8a9aca4d23f4c1d60","tid":2138051,"uid":162103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:50:19.000Z","msg":"別讓江江跑掉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:58:16.000Z","msg":"小江<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ce850e690cf55f00a488bb8c1d80e2a9a77204","tid":2138051,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218cc89686cda0ec105ea9d911e7b75fe03a814a","tid":2138051,"uid":230298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:07:13.000Z","msg":"高振邦呢啲文官仲跑得郁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}